T02D1862:64b-1: gu hya dzam bha la s'a dha nam /
T02D1862:64b-3: gsang ba'i dzam bha la'i sgrub thabs /
T02D1862:64b-4: 'phags pa dzam bha la la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1862:64b-5: de la thog mar re zhig sngags pas gdong gi gtsang sbra la sogs pa byas nas /
T02D1862:64b-6: skye bo med pa'i sa phyogs su bde ba'i stan la gnas te /
T02D1862:64b-7: bdag gis rje btsun dzam bha la mnyes par byas
T02D1862:64b-8: la sems can thams cad mchog gi bde ba la
T02D1862:64b-9: sbyar bar bya'o zhes byang chub kyi sems bskyed la
T02D1862:64b-10: / rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la dzam gi yi ge ser po bltas te /
T02D1862:64b-11: de'i 'od kyis bla ma dang sangs rgyas dang byang
T02D1862:64b-12: chub sems dpa' dang rje btsun dzam bha la mdun
T02D1862:64b-13: du bsams la yang dag par mchod de phyag byas
T02D1862:64b-14: te / sdig pa bshags pa la sogs pa byas te /
T02D1862:64b-15: 'jigs pas sdig pa thams cad bshags par bya //
T02D1862:64b-16: dga' bas 'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rang //
T02D1862:64b-17: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
T02D1862:64b-18: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems ni rnam par gzung //
T02D1862:64b-19: de'i rjes su byams pa dang snying rje dang dga' ba dang btang snyoms bsgom par bya'o //
T02D1862:64b-20: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa
T02D1862:64b-21: a'atma ko& ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis thams cad stong
T02D1862:64b-22: pa nyid du bsgom par bya'o //
T02D1862:64b-23: de'i rjes su smon lam gyi shugs kyis nam kham
T02D1862:64b-24: bam lam gi sa bon las skyes pa'i sna tshogs
T02D1862:64b-25: padma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i steng du zla ba la
T02D1862:64b-26: dzam ser po las skyes pa'i bcom ldan 'das dzam
T02D1862:64b-27: bha la bsgom par bya ste /
T02D1862:64b-28: rgyan thams cad 'dzin pa gser gyi kha dog can /
T02D1862:64b-30: g-yon pa dang g-yas pa'i phyag dag gis sre mo dang sa bon gang ba 'dzin pa /
T02D1862:64b-31: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi cod pan autpala'i phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
T02D1862:64b-32: shar la sogs pa'i 'dab ma rnams su nor bu bzang po dang /
T02D1862:64b-36: me la sogs pa'i 'dab ma rnams la rna rgyan kor sleb dang /
T02D1862:65a-1: pa'i dbang phyug ste bshad pa'i rim pas der de ltar nor rgyun ma dang /
T02D1862:65a-10: gnod sbyin mo 'di dag rnams bsam par bya'o //
T02D1862:65a-11: nor rgyun ma dang dzam bha la lhan cig tu'o //
T02D1862:65a-12: gnod sbyin ma thams cad nor rgyun ma bzhin no //
T02D1862:65a-13: gnod sbyin thams cad dzam bha la bzhin no //
T02D1862:65a-14: 'di ltar bsams te sngags bzlas par bya ste de la gnod sbyin rnams kyi ni /
T02D1862:65a-15: aom dzam bha la dza lendra ya dha nam me de hi de hi sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-16: aom ma ni bha dr'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-17: aom p'urnna bha dr'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-18: aom dha na d'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-19: aom bee shra ba n'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-20: aom pi tsi kundi li ne sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-21: aom ki li m'a li ne sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-22: aom mu khendr'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-23: aom tsa rendr'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-24: de nas gnod sbyin mo rnams kyi sngags ni /
T02D1862:65a-25: aom ba su dha rin+yee sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-30: aom su bha dr'a yee sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-33: aom sa ra sva tyee sv'a h'a /
T02D1862:65a-34: 'di lta bu thun gsum du bzlas pas chu khyor
T02D1862:65a-35: ba brgya rtsa brgyad ster ba la 'jig rten gsum
T02D1862:65a-37: tho rangs bya rog mi grag par chu'i dbus su
T02D1862:65a-38: bzlas na nor 'dzad pa med cing 'phel bar 'gyur
T02D1862:65a-39: ro // de nas gser la sogs pa'i 'dab ma la nor rgyun ma dang /
T02D1862:65a-40: gnod sbyin mo lhan cig pa dang /
T02D1862:65a-41: 'dab ma gnyis pa la bcom ldan 'das dzam bha
T02D1862:65a-42: la la gnod sbyin gyis yongs su bskor ba bis
T02D1862:65a-43: nas mar dang sbrang rtsi dang ka ras sbyar te
T02D1862:65a-44: / rab gnas legs par byas la mnyes par byas na grub pa chen po brgyad ster ro //
T02D1862:65a-45: zho dang bu ram dang bcas pa'i zan dang sha dang /
T02D1862:65a-46: chang spangs pa'i gtor ma bzlas pa'i sngags kyis rgyun du sbyin no //
T02D1862:65a-47: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyis mdzad pa /
T02D1862:65a-48: gsang ba'i dzam bha la'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02D1862:65a-50: // / mkhas pa chen po dza ya se na'i zhal snga nas dang /
